xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Number</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">1</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Day</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">Monday</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Colors</p><div class=\"mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 ring-1 ring-slate-200\">Blue</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-white px-3 py-1 text-sm text-slate-700 ring-1 ring-slate-200\">Gold</span></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Lucky Stone</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900\">Topaz</p></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 bg-slate-50 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Life Path Number</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900\">3</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-4 rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700\"><span class=\"font-semibold text-slate-900\">Numerology meaning:</span> <!-- -->Number 1 symbolizes leadership and legacy — aligning with the Imran lineage in Islamic tradition.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-heart h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M2 9.5a5.5 5.5 0 0 1 9.591-3.676.56.56 0 0 0 .818 0A5.49 5.49 0 0 1 22 9.5c0 2.29-1.5 4-3 5.5l-5.492 5.313a2 2 0 0 1-3 .019L5 15c-1.5-1.5-3-3.2-3-5.5\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Personality</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Personality Traits</h2></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-2\"><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Loyal</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Spiritual</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Noble</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">Honest</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">I = Inspiring presence</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">M = Morally strong</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">R = Responsible soul</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">A = Affectionate heart</span><span class=\"rounded-full bg-emerald-50 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-emerald-800 ring-1 ring-emerald-100\">N = Noble in thoughts</span></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-book-text h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2H19a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v18a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H6.5a1 1 0 0 1 0-5H20\"></path><path d=\"M8 11h8\"></path><path d=\"M8 7h6\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Spiritual</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Spiritual Significance</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-slate-800 leading-7\">Symbolizes spiritual leadership, generational blessings, and family honor — a name tied to prophetic ancestry.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-shield h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 13c0 5-3.5 7.5-7.66 8.95a1 1 0 0 1-.67-.01C7.5 20.5 4 18 4 13V6a1 1 0 0 1 1-1c2 0 4.5-1.2 6.24-2.72a1.17 1.17 0 0 1 1.52 0C14.51 3.81 17 5 19 5a1 1 0 0 1 1 1z\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Cultural Context</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Cultural Significance</h2></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\"><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\">Imran is a name deeply rooted in Islamic culture and carries a rich heritage. It is not only the name of the revered prophet&#x27;s father but is also used as a given name for boys in various Muslim communities around the world. The name represents strong roots, noble lineage, and prosperity, making it a proud and meaningful name for many families.</div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\">In Islamic beliefs, the name Imran holds significant spiritual value. It is mentioned in Surah Al-Imran, the third chapter of the Quran, and is linked to Maryam, the mother of Prophet Isa, who was born miraculously to her father Imran. The name signifies righteousness and purity, being associated with such a revered figure in Islamic history. Imran&#x27;s spiritual significance is a reminder of the importance of righteous deeds, a strong and noble character, and a deep connection to one&#x27;s ancestors, as their legacy continues through generations.</div><p class=\"rounded-3xl bg-emerald-50 p-4 text-sm text-emerald-800\">Traditional Islamic naming context<!-- --> — Traditional Islamic name with deep spiritual significance in Islamic culture</p></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M11.017 2.814a1 1 0 0 1 1.966 0l1.051 5.558a2 2 0 0 0 1.594 1.594l5.558 1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.966l-5.558 1.051a2 2 0 0 0-1.594 1.594l-1.051 5.558a1 1 0 0 1-1.966 0l-1.051-5.558a2 2 0 0 0-1.594-1.594l-5.558-1.051a1 1 0 0 1 0-1.966l5.558-1.051a2 2 0 0 0 1.594-1.594z\"></path><path d=\"M20 2v4\"></path><path d=\"M22 4h-4\"></path><circle cx=\"4\" cy=\"20\" r=\"2\"></circle></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Spiritual</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Spiritual Symbolism</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-slate-800 leading-7\">The name Imran in Islamic tradition symbolizes faith, patience, and devotion. It is believed that Imran, the father of Prophetasas (Ibrahim&#x27;s son Isa or Jesus), embodied these virtues while raising his son in the service of God.</div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-trending-up h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M16 7h6v6\"></path><path d=\"m22 7-8.5 8.5-5-5L2 17\"></path></svg></div><div><p class=\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\">Popularity</p><h2 class=\"text-xl font-semibold\">Popularity by Region</h2></div></div><div class=\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4 text-slate-700 leading-7\"><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Saudi Arabia</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->88</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">Pakistan</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->82</span></div><div class=\"flex justify-between py-2 border-b border-slate-200 last:border-0\"><span class=\"font-medium\">UAE</span><span class=\"text-slate-600\">Score: <!-- -->81</span></div></div></section><section class=\"nv-card\"><div class=\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\"><div class=\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-award h-5 w-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m15.477 12.89 1.515 8.526a.5.5 0 0 1-.81.47l-3.58-2.687a1 1 0 0 0-1.197 0l-3.586 2.686a.5.5 0 0 1-.81-.469l1.514-8.526\"></path>