n various Muslim communities around the world. The name represents strong roots, noble lineage, and prosperity, making it a proud and meaningful name for many families.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl bg-slate-50 p-4\",\"children\":\"In Islamic beliefs, the name Imran holds significant spiritual value. It is mentioned in Surah Al-Imran, the third chapter of the Quran, and is linked to Maryam, the mother of Prophet Isa, who was born miraculously to her father Imran. The name signifies righteousness and purity, being associated with such a revered figure in Islamic history. Imran's spiritual significance is a reminder of the importance of righteous deeds, a strong and noble character, and a deep connection to one's ancestors, as their legacy continues through generations.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl bg-emerald-50 p-4 text-sm text-emerald-800\",\"children\":[\"Traditional Islamic naming context\",\" — Traditional Islamic name with deep spiritual significance in Islamic culture\"]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]]}]\n62:[\"$\",\"$L70\",null,{\"className\":\"my-6\",\"minHeight\":\"90px\",\"instanceId\":\"name-detail-mid\"}]\n63:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"nv-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1a\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$5e:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\",\"children\":\"Spiritual\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Spiritual Symbolism\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{