s, a strong and noble character, and a deep connection to one's ancestors, as their legacy continues through generations.\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl bg-emerald-50 p-4 text-sm text-emerald-800\",\"children\":[\"Traditional Islamic naming context\",\" — Traditional Islamic name with deep spiritual significance in Islamic culture\"]}],\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\"]}]]}]\n62:[\"$\",\"$L70\",null,{\"className\":\"my-6\",\"minHeight\":\"90px\",\"instanceId\":\"name-detail-mid\"}]\n63:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"nv-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1a\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefined\",\"iconNode\":\"$5e:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:children:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-sparkles h-5 w-5\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-slate-500\",\"children\":\"Spiritual\"}],[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-xl font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Spiritual Symbolism\"}],\"$undefined\"]}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-3xl bg-amber-50 p-4 text-slate-800 leading-7\",\"children\":\"The name Imran in Islamic tradition symbolizes faith, patience, and devotion. It is believed that Imran, the father of Prophetasas (Ibrahim's son Isa or Jesus), embodied these virtues while raising his son in the service of God.\"}]]}]\n64:[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"className\":\"nv-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-5 flex items-start gap-3 text-slate-900\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex h-11 w-11 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-amber-100 text-amber-700 shadow-sm\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L1a\",null,{\"ref\":\"$undefi