nsible soul\",\"A = Affectionate heart\",\"N = Noble in thoughts\"],\"lucky_number\":1,\"lucky_day\":\"Monday\",\"lucky_colors\":[\"Blue\",\"Gold\"],\"lucky_stone\":\"Topaz\",\"life_path_number\":3,\"numerology_meaning\":\"Number 1 symbolizes leadership and legacy — aligning with the Imran lineage in Islamic tradition.\",\"in_arabic\":{\"name\":\"عمران\",\"meaning\":\"عمرを持つ、繁栄する、高齢者\"},\"in_urdu\":{\"name\":\"عمران\",\"meaning\":\"عمریں رکھنے والا، بڑھیا، خوشحال\"},\"in_hindi\":{\"name\":\"इमरान\",\"meaning\":\"लंबी उम्र वाला, समृद्ध, खुशहाल\"},\"in_pashto\":{\"name\":\"عمران\",\"meaning\":\"د اوږد عمر لرونکی، شتمن\"},\"in_english\":{\"name\":\"Imran\",\"meaning\":\"Long-lived, prosperous, rich\"},\"pronunciation\":{\"english\":\"im-RAN\",\"ipa\":\"/ɪmˈrɑːn/\"},\"celebrity_usage\":[\"Imran Khan (former cricketer & PM of Pakistan)\",\"Imran Abbas (actor)\"],\"social_tags\":[\"#ImranMeaning\",\"#IslamicBabyNames\",\"#ArabicNames\",\"#MuslimNames\",\"#Imran\"],\"name_variations\":[],\"popularity_score\":58,\"popularity_by_region\":[{\"region\":\"Saudi Arabia\",\"country_code\":\"SA\",\"score\":88,\"year\":2024},{\"region\":\"Pakistan\",\"country_code\":\"PK\",\"score\":82,\"year\":2024},{\"region\":\"UAE\",\"country_code\":\"AE\",\"score\":81,\"year\":2024}],\"seo\":{\"title\":\"Imran Name Meaning | Islam Baby Names 2026\",\"meta_description\":\"Discover the complete meaning of Imran, a beautiful Islam name meaning \\\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\\\". Learn about its Arabic origin and spiritual significance.\",\"meta_keywords\":\"Imran, Islam name, baby names, Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father, Islam baby names, name meaning\",\"description_paragraph\":\"Imran is a meaningful Islam name of Arabic origin that means \\\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\\\". Imran is a revered Quranic name meaning 'prosperity' or 'long-lived'. It is the name of the father of Maryam (Mary), the mother of Prophet Isa (Jesus), mentioned in Surah Al-Imran. The name reflects righteousness, legacy, and noble lineage.\",\"keywords\":[\"Imran\",\"Islam name\",\"baby names\",\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\",\"Islam tradition\",\"Arabic origin\"],\"faq\":[{\"q\":\"What is the meaning of Imran in Islam tradition?\",\"a\":\"Imran is a beautiful Islam name meaning \\\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\\\". This name has deep spiritual significance in Islam tradition.\"},{\"q\":\"Is Imran a good Islam name for a baby?\",\"a\":\"Yes, Imran is an excellent Islam name choice. It carries positive meanings and cultural significance.\"},{\"q\":\"What is the origin of the name Imran?\",\"a\":\"The name Imran has Arabic origins and is deeply rooted in Islam tradition.\"},{\"q\":\"How do you pronounce Imran correctly?\",\"a\":\"Imran is pronounced im-RAN in English.\"},{\"q\":\"What are the spiritual benefits of naming a child Imran?\",\"a\":\"Naming a child Imran brings blessings. The meaning \\\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\\\" inspires positive qualities.\"},{\"q\":\"How popular is the name Imran?\",\"a\":\"Imran is well-regarded in Islam communities worldwide.\"}],\"seo_score\":90,\"focus_keyword\":\"Imran meaning\",\"secondary_keywords\":[\"Islam name Imran\",\"Imran meaning\",\"Imran origin\"]},\"monetization\":{\"propush_trigger\":true,\"exit_ad_enabled\":true,\"ads_enabled\":true},\"cultural_impact\":\"Imran is a name deeply rooted in Islamic culture and carries a rich heritage. It is not only the name of the revered prophet's father but is also used as a given name for boys in various Muslim communities around the world. The name represents strong roots, noble lineage, and prosperity, making it a proud and meaningful name for many families.\",\"spiritual_significance\":\"In Islamic beliefs, the name Imran holds significant spiritual value. It is mentioned in Surah Al-Imran, the third chapter of the Quran, and is linked to Maryam, the mother of Prophet Isa, who was born miraculously to her father Imran. The name signifies righteousness and purity, being associated with such a revered figure in Islamic history. Imran's spiritual significance is a reminder of the importance of righteous deeds, a strong and noble character, and a deep connection to one's ancestors, as their legacy continues through generations.\",\"islamic_reference\":{\"is_quranic\":false,\"note\":\"Traditional Islamic name with deep spiritual significance in Islamic culture\"},\"historical_references\":[{\"reference\":\"Historical records show that Imran was a prophet in Islamic tradition, mentioned in the Quran. The name Imran carried significant weight in that era.\",\"time_period\":\"7th century\",\"context\":\"Imran is mentioned in the Quran as the father of Prophet Isa (Jesus) and wife of Prophet Hussain's mother, Asma bint Imran.\"}],\"modern_usage\":{\"trends\":[\"Imran is a common name in the Muslim world.\",\"Imran is the name of a cricket team in Pakistan.\"],\"platforms\":[\"Imran Khan is a prominent Pakistani politician and former cricket captain.\",\"Imran Ashraf is a Pakistani actor and model.\"],\"modern_context\":\"The name Imran remains relevant in modern Muslim society, representing a bridge between traditional Islamic values and contemporary life. It is widely discussed on digital platforms and continues to be a popular choice for families seeking meaningful Islamic names.\"},\"name_in_real_life\":{\"person_name\":\"Yusuf Imran\",\"location\":\"Karachi, Pakistan\",\"story\":\"Yusuf Imran from Karachi, Pakistan embodies the meaning of Imran - \\\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\\\". Growing up, they were known for their strong character and deep faith, always striving to live up to the beautiful significance of their name.\"},\"spiritual_symbolism\":\"The name Imran in Islamic tradition symbolizes faith, patience, and devotion. It is believed that Imran, the father of Prophetasas (Ibrahim's son Isa or Jesus), embodied these virtues while raising his son in the service of God.\",\"created_at\":\"2025-06-30T18:30:00+05:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2025-12-22T04:53:14.049Z\",\"advanced_seo\":{\"technical_seo\":{\"page_load_speed\":\"optimized\",\"mobile_friendly\":true,\"schema_markup\":true,\"ssl_certificate\":true,\"cdn_optimized\":true},\"content_seo\":{\"word_count\":1449,\"readability_score\":\"A+\",\"keyword_density\":\"optimal\",\"internal_linking\":true},\"performance_metrics\":{\"core_web_vitals\":\"excellent\",\"bounce_rate_prediction\":\"low\",\"engagement_time\":\"high\"}},\"structured_data\":{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"Imran\",\"description\":\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\",\"additionalName\":[],\"knowsLanguage\":[\"English\",\"Urdu\",\"Arabic\",\"Pashto\",\"Hindi\"],\"religion\":\"Islam\",\"gender\":\"Male\",\"origin\":\"Arabic\"},\"user_engagement\":{\"interactive_features\":{\"name_calculator\":true,\"meaning_quiz\":true,\"pronunciation_tool\":true,\"compatibility_checker\":true},\"community_features\":{\"user_stories\":[],\"rating_system\":true,\"comment_section\":true},\"personalization\":{\"favorite_lists\":true,\"name_comparison\":true,\"save_preferences\":true}},\"social_optimization\":{\"social_media_cards\":{\"facebook\":{\"title\":\"Beautiful Name: Imran\",\"description\":\"Discover the meaning of Imran - \\\"Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\\\"\",\"image\":\"/images/social/imran-facebook.jpg\"},\"twitter\":{\"title\":\"Imran - Name Meaning\",\"description\":\"Learn about the beautiful name Imran\",\"image\":\"/images/social/imran-twitter.jpg\"},\"instagram\":{\"title\":\"Imran\",\"description\":\"Name meaning: Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\",\"image\":\"/images/social/imran-instagram.jpg\"}},\"sharing_optimization\":{\"whatsapp_message\":\"Check out this beautiful name: Imran - Meaning: Prosperity, Long-lived, Name of a Prophet's Father\",\"email_sub